<div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl p-4 sm:p-6">
    <h1 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600">Answers about accounts, sessions, flags, and data privacy.</p>
  
    <div class="mt-6 space-y-3">
      <!-- Reusable FAQ item pattern -->
      <details class="group rounded-xl bg-white ring-1 ring-gray-200 shadow-sm open:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer list-none px-4 py-3 flex items-start justify-between gap-4">
          <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900">How do I create an account?</span>
          <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-gray-400 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-width="1.6" d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="px-4 pb-4 text-sm text-gray-700">
          Go to <a class="text-blue-600 hover:underline" href="/register">Register</a>, fill in your details, and submit.
          You’ll be signed in automatically after creating the account.
        </div>
      </details>
  
      <details class="group rounded-xl bg-white ring-1 ring-gray-200 shadow-sm">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer list-none px-4 py-3 flex items-start justify-between gap-4">
          <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900">What counts toward the church goal?</span>
          <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-gray-400 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-width="1.6" d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="px-4 pb-4 text-sm text-gray-700">
          The goal is based on <span class="font-medium">Gospel + Witness</span> totals from approved, non-flagged sessions this year.
        </div>
      </details>
  
      <details class="group rounded-xl bg-white ring-1 ring-gray-200 shadow-sm">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer list-none px-4 py-3 flex items-start justify-between gap-4">
          <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900">Why was my session flagged?</span>
          <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-gray-400 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-width="1.6" d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="px-4 pb-4 text-sm text-gray-700">
          Entries may be auto-flagged when numbers exceed safe thresholds or appear duplicate.
          An admin reviews flagged sessions; approved ones will then appear in your lists and totals.
        </div>
      </details>
  
      <details class="group rounded-xl bg-white ring-1 ring-gray-200 shadow-sm">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer list-none px-4 py-3 flex items-start justify-between gap-4">
          <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900">Can I enter future dates?</span>
          <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-gray-400 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-width="1.6" d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="px-4 pb-4 text-sm text-gray-700">
          No. The form and server validation block future date/times.
        </div>
      </details>
  
      <details class="group rounded-xl bg-white ring-1 ring-gray-200 shadow-sm">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer list-none px-4 py-3 flex items-start justify-between gap-4">
          <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900">What do the metrics mean?</span>
          <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-gray-400 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-width="1.6" d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="px-4 pb-4 text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-2">
          <p><span class="font-medium">Engaged:</span> meaningful conversation or contact.</p>
          <p><span class="font-medium">Gospel:</span> clear presentation of the Good News about Jesus.</p>
          <p><span class="font-medium">Witness:</span> personal testimony about Jesus and what He’s done in your life.</p>
          <p><span class="font-medium">Decisions:</span> indicated a decision to follow Jesus or recommit.</p>
          <p><span class="font-medium">Prayed:</span> you prayed with someone.</p>
        </div>
      </details>
  
      <details class="group rounded-xl bg-white ring-1 ring-gray-200 shadow-sm">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer list-none px-4 py-3 flex items-start justify-between gap-4">
          <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900">Who can see my data?</span>
          <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-gray-400 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-width="1.6" d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="px-4 pb-4 text-sm text-gray-700">
          Only you and approved church admins see identifiable data. Public dashboards show totals only.
          See our <a class="text-blue-600 hover:underline" href="/terms">Terms & Data Policy</a>.
        </div>
      </details>
  
      <details class="group rounded-xl bg-white ring-1 ring-gray-200 shadow-sm">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer list-none px-4 py-3 flex items-start justify-between gap-4">
          <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900">How do I edit or delete a session?</span>
          <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-gray-400 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-width="1.6" d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="px-4 pb-4 text-sm text-gray-700">
            Contact your church admin.
        </div>
      </details>
  
      <details class="group rounded-xl bg-white ring-1 ring-gray-200 shadow-sm">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer list-none px-4 py-3 flex items-start justify-between gap-4">
          <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900">Why can’t a number be higher than Engaged?</span>
          <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-gray-400 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-width="1.6" d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="px-4 pb-4 text-sm text-gray-700">
          To keep reports realistic, Gospel, Witness, Decisions, and Prayed cannot exceed the number of people Engaged.
        </div>
      </details>
  
      <details class="group rounded-xl bg-white ring-1 ring-gray-200 shadow-sm">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer list-none px-4 py-3 flex items-start justify-between gap-4">
          <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900">How do I get help?</span>
          <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-gray-400 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-width="1.6" d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="px-4 pb-4 text-sm text-gray-700">
          Contact your church admin.
        </div>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
  